! Offline Installation

The Darts Scoreboard is available as a standalone HTML file that works completely offline.

!! Quick Download

* [[Latest Release|https://dxcsithlord.github.io/Darts-score-board-tiddlywiki/releases/darts-scoreboard-latest.html]] - Download the most recent version
* [[GitHub Releases|https://github.com/dxcSithLord/Darts-score-board-tiddlywiki/releases]] - Browse all versions

!! Installation Steps

# Download `darts-scoreboard-latest.html` (or a specific version)
# Save the file to your local machine (Desktop, Documents, etc.)
# Double-click the file or open it with your browser

That's it! No installation, no setup, no internet required.

!! Using via file:// URI

You can open the file directly in your browser using a file:// URI:

''Windows'':
```
file:///C:/Users/YourName/Desktop/darts-scoreboard.html
```

''macOS'':
```
file:///Users/YourName/Desktop/darts-scoreboard.html
```

''Linux'':
```
file:///home/username/Desktop/darts-scoreboard.html
```

!! Features of Offline Version

* No internet connection required
* All CSS and JavaScript embedded in single file
* Works in Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge
* No external dependencies or CDN links
* Version information included in file header
* Portable - copy to USB drive, share with friends

!! Important Notes

!!! localStorage Limitations
Score history may not persist when using file:// URIs in some browsers due to security restrictions. This is a browser security feature, not a bug.

!!! Browser Compatibility
For best results, use:
* Google Chrome (recommended)
* Mozilla Firefox (recommended)
* Microsoft Edge
* Safari (may have file:// restrictions)

!!! Updates
To get the latest features and bug fixes, simply re-download the latest version from the links above. Your old file can be deleted or kept as a backup.
